| Key | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL` | Supabase project URL |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` | Supabase anon key |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY` | Client-side Google Maps (legacy, in `lib/google.ts`) |
| `GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY` | Server-side Google Places API |
| `CQC_API_KEY` | CQC API subscription key |
| Firebase keys | Hardcoded in `lib/firebase.ts` |

