## 🔲 What's NOT Done / Next Steps

### High Priority
| # | Task | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | **Scraped leads UI integration** | API exists (`/api/leads/scraped`) but the frontend `LeadTable` doesn't have a tab/mode to display scraped leads from Doctify |
| 2 | **GoPrivate scraper** | The schema supports `goprivate` source, but no scraper script exists for it yet |
| 3 | **Duplicate `Lead` interface** | The `Lead` interface is duplicated across 4 files — should be centralized into a shared types file |
| 4 | **Firebase → Supabase auth migration** | Firebase is still used for auth while Supabase is used for data. Consider consolidating to Supabase Auth |
| 5 | **API key security** | Firebase config is hardcoded in `lib/firebase.ts`. Google Places API key is exposed client-side in `lib/google.ts` (server-side route exists but both paths are active) |

### Medium Priority
| # | Task | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| 6 | **Error handling & loading states** | Some API errors lack user-friendly feedback |
| 7 | **Responsive design polish** | Desktop-first — mobile experience could be improved |
| 8 | **Rate limiting** | No rate limiting on API routes — could be abused |
| 9 | **Vercel deployment** | DEPLOY.md exists but references old Firebase env vars; needs updating for Supabase vars |
| 10 | **Search debouncing** | Live search could benefit from debounced input |

### Low Priority / Nice-to-Have
| # | Task | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| 11 | **Dashboard analytics** | No analytics/metrics page for lead generation stats |
| 12 | **User roles & permissions** | No admin vs regular user distinction |
| 13 | **Lead tagging/notes** | Users can't add custom tags or notes to saved leads |
| 14 | **Email/SMS outreach** | No integration for contacting leads directly |
| 15 | **Map view** | Lat/Lng data exists from CQC but no map visualization |

